{"tid":1130022,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"［裝修佬入］虛心請教新樓裝修","createTime":"2019-04-28T17:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T11:43:24.000Z","uid":194140,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1bb83b422926190e810ae758dd79e1ac2d40d85e","tid":1130022,"uid":194140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T17:58:13.000Z","msg":"今日同個做地盤的uncle吹水，佢話新樓D裝修好行貨，收樓後全部牆都要批過曬重新搞一次油一次，唔係會好快甩晒皮。然後地板好多時都要自己再鋪過先住得人。我就問如果大發展商都信唔過？佢話係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好想知而家D樓下下成千萬，真係買完重要裝？！<br />\n定佢無料扮四條其實未住過新樓呢？<br />\n佢話曬都半個行家我唔敢反駁佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f3cd295f0318aaef935009600a196dad1a2cdc","tid":1130022,"uid":42268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T18:00:03.000Z","msg":"執漏啫"},{"pid":"8c078c8cae123e18dde0bad90e2a87e8b91ccb40","tid":1130022,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T18:04:40.000Z","msg":"以為就話新地樓手工好，現在全部都差架啦"},{"pid":"cf1010a5f9dc86706e14e0d32179d62b5d9132ec","tid":1130022,"uid":36234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T18:06:53.000Z","msg":"我覺得打算長住既不如洗少少錢，油漆鋪磚幾萬蚊搞掂"},{"pid":"0d3071c3ebe4fa7228740e35f6277fee6cb7a915","tid":1130022,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T18:07:52.000Z","msg":"鋪磚都係一班人鋪晒 唔會走去批盪 <br />\n<br />\n熟手唔等於手工靚 手工靚要時間整"},{"pid":"fcefafbf4763e637d5c6b26716ceb0d442e89c5e","tid":1130022,"uid":194140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf1010a5f9dc86706e14e0d32179d62b5d9132ec","tid":1130022,"uid":36234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T18:06:53.000Z","msg":"我覺得打算長住既不如洗少少錢，油漆鋪磚幾萬蚊搞掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T18:13:42.000Z","msg":"原裝真係咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全新再整一次好似好唔環保"},{"pid":"552f710f3bcd5caa366def6fb4b5d1159f56aeac","tid":1130022,"uid":245106,"like":2,"dislike":0,"scor